00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,830
Ya.

245
00:14:43,810 --> 00:14:45,440
Beritahukan semuanya kepada Mikey.

246
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,640
Okey.

247
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,290
