Aku nak selamatkan Hina.

292
00:16:58,530 --> 00:17:01,890
Aku kena menghalang pergaduhan dengan Moebius.

293
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:08,980
Mikey.

294
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:20,270
