335
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:44,990
Mikey.

336
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:46,240
Apa?

337
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,570
Kenchin.

338
00:19:47,570 --> 00:19:49,490
